Robbie Williams New Album To Be Released by Universal Music

-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 
2011-10-22T07:45:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-22/robbie-williams-new-album-to-be-released-by-universal-music.html
British singer  Robbie Williams ’
forthcoming solo album will be released by  Universal Music  Group
next autumn, according to a  statement  on Williams’ website.  The record will be Williams’ first studio album since 2009,
the statement said. The singer recently reunited with his former
band Take That.  The Sunday Times reported on Sept. 11 that EMI Group Ltd.
wanted to re-sign Williams to increase the value of the company
before a sale this fall.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Martin in London at 
